CLDL: Direxion Daily Cloud Computing Bull 2X Shares

The fund, under normal circumstances, invests at least 80% of its net assets in financial instruments, such as swap agreements, securities of the index, ETFs that track the index and other financial instruments that provide daily leveraged exposure to the index or to ETFs that track the index. The index is provided by Indxx, LLC and includes domestic companies that deliver cloud computing infrastructure, platforms, or services. The fund is non-diversified.
